  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HOW WELL DO YOU KNOW YOUR TV SHOWS?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your knowledge with some of the most popular television series of all time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Television Trivia has never been so much fun. Challenge yourself in Single Player, or host a trivia night with friends and family in Party Mode (up to 4 players). Choose a show and answer thousands of multiple-choice questions—perfect for quick pick‑up‑and‑play sessions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Includes 9 fan‑favorite TV shows:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Simpsons</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game of Thrones</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Office</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Friends</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Star Trek</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>South Park</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grey’s Anatomy</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Sopranos</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seinfeld</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Player Mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party Mode (Up to 4 Players)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thousands of multiple-choice questions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for group trivia nights</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick, pick-up-and-play sessions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gamepad support</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So what are you waiting for? Download now and get your brain ready for Television Trivia!</p>",
